{"text_id":54700,"tokens":["The"," issue"," of"," whether"," cell"," phone"," usage"," should"," be"," prohibited"," while"," driving"," has"," been"," a"," topic"," of"," intense"," debate"," in"," recent"," years","."," With"," the"," increasing"," number"," of"," vehicular"," accidents"," caused"," by"," distracted"," driving",","," many"," argue"," that"," a"," ban"," on"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," is"," necessary"," to"," ensure"," road"," safety","."," However",","," others"," contend"," that"," such"," a"," ban"," inf","ringes"," on"," personal"," freedoms"," and"," may"," not"," effectively"," reduce"," accidents","."," In"," this"," essay",","," I"," will"," examine"," both"," sides"," of"," the"," argument"," and"," present"," a"," conclusion"," based"," on"," the"," evidence",".","\n\n","On"," the"," one"," hand",","," those"," who"," support"," a"," ban"," on"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," argue"," that"," it"," is"," a"," crucial"," step"," towards"," reducing"," the"," number"," of"," accidents"," caused"," by"," distracted"," driving","."," According"," to"," the"," National"," Highway"," Traffic"," Safety"," Administration"," (","NH","TSA","),"," in"," ","2","0","1","9",","," ","3",",","1","4","2"," people"," were"," killed"," in"," motor"," vehicle"," crashes"," involving"," distracted"," drivers","."," Text","ing",","," talking"," on"," a"," cell"," phone",","," and"," other"," forms"," of"," distracted"," driving"," are"," major"," contributors"," to"," these"," statistics","."," A"," ban"," on"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," would"," reduce"," the"," number"," of"," distractions"," and",","," therefore",","," the"," number"," of"," accidents",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," studies"," have"," shown"," that"," using"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving"," can"," be"," as"," dangerous"," as"," drunk"," driving","."," A"," study"," by"," the"," University"," of"," Utah"," found"," that"," drivers"," who"," text"," are"," ","2","3"," times"," more"," likely"," to"," be"," involved"," in"," a"," crash"," or"," near","-","crash"," event"," compared"," to"," non","-","di","stra","cted"," drivers","."," Furthermore",","," a"," study"," by"," the"," Virginia"," Tech"," Transportation"," Institute"," found"," that"," texting"," while"," driving"," takes"," a"," driver","'","s"," eyes"," off"," the"," road"," for"," an"," average"," of"," ","4",".","6"," seconds",","," which"," is"," the"," equivalent"," of"," driving"," the"," length"," of"," a"," football"," field"," at"," ","5","5"," mph","."," These"," statistics"," highlight"," the"," dangers"," of"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," and"," the"," need"," for"," a"," ban",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," those"," who"," oppose"," a"," ban"," on"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," argue"," that"," it"," inf","ringes"," on"," personal"," freedoms","."," They"," contend"," that"," adults"," should"," be"," responsible"," enough"," to"," make"," their"," own"," decisions"," about"," whether"," or"," not"," to"," use"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving","."," They"," also"," argue"," that"," a"," ban"," on"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," may"," not"," be"," effective"," in"," reducing"," accidents","."," For"," instance",","," drivers"," may"," still"," use"," their"," phones"," while"," stopped"," at"," red"," lights"," or"," in"," heavy"," traffic",","," which"," can"," be"," just"," as"," dangerous"," as"," using"," a"," phone"," while"," moving",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," opponents"," of"," a"," ban"," on"," cell"," phone"," usage"," while"," driving"," argue"," that"," there"," are"," better"," ways"," to"," address"," the"," issue"," of"," distracted"," driving","."," For"," example",","," many"," cars"," now"," come"," equipped"," with"," hands","-","free"," technology"," that"," allows"," drivers"," to"," make"," calls"," and"," send"," te